rows.label: qev061002_MSG0017
rows.name: Aa...nngh... *fsssh* C-can't...go on...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0018
rows.name: *fsssssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0019
rows.name: Wh-what? *fsssh* Strong voltant waves...nearby...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0020
rows.name:
Oh! I feel voltant filling every inch of my body! *fsssh*
It's the raw force of a true zirtodiamond![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0120
rows.name: Nrraaah! AaaaaAAAAAAAH! *fsssh* *fsssh* *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0021
rows.name: Hrrngh... Ah... *fsssssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0022
rows.name:
...Huh? You're the mirage I saw. *fsssh*
Wait, did YOU bring me this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0030
rows.name: Demand[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0031
rows.name: Insist that Toluera hand over Golbogga's legacy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0040
rows.name: Worry[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Toluera if he's feeling all right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0023
rows.name:
It seems that you really do exist after all. *fsssh*
Which means I'm bound to honor my promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0024
rows.name:
This disk is what you're after, yes? *fsssh*
It is yours by rights.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0025
rows.name:
Thanks to you. I don't know that I've ever felt so
thoroughly full of voltant. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0026
rows.name: ...Which means I have a promise to keep. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0027
rows.name:
This disk is what you're after, is it not? *fsssh*
Take it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0028
rows.name:
*fsssh* ...Though I still don't understand why a human
would desire such a thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0029
rows.name: ...What?! Feloran sent you?! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0030
rows.name:
Urgh. If I'd known that, I wouldn't have handed it over
so easily. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0031
rows.name:
...Perhaps it's not too late though. *fsssh*
For you see, if a Golbogga fanatic like him gets his
hands on that, he'll spread dangerous rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0032
rows.name:
So just hand it back to me. *fsssh* Do that,
and I'll prove once and for all Golbogga doesn't exist![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0050
rows.name: Refuse[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0051
rows.name: Firmly turn down Toluera's request.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0060
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0061
rows.name: Ask what Toluera has against Feloran.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0033
rows.name:
*fsssh* You're no different from the other Zaruboggan—
blindly believing in something nobody's ever seen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0034
rows.name:
Fine then! Take it! *fsssh* But I'll tell you now,
the only thing you're going to prove with what's
on there is that Golbogga never existed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0035
rows.name:
Because he's a liar! *fsssh* He demands that all believe
in his precious Golbogga when it's clearly a fantasy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0036
rows.name:
*fsssh* My claim was scientific. I said Zaruboggan
gradually evolved from microorganisms floating in
voltant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0037
rows.name:
But those zealots called me a heretic and silenced my
work. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0038
rows.name:
*fsssh* So I stole this disk from their grand cathedral on
Bedun in order to have my revenge.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0039
rows.name:
...Actually, could I possibly get you to help me unlock
its contents? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0040
rows.name: You and I shall expose Feloran's lies together! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0070
rows.name: Refuse[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0071
rows.name: Firmly turn down Toluera's request.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0080
rows.name: Accept[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0081
rows.name: Agree to help Toluera.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0041
rows.name:
*fsssh* You're no different from the other Zaruboggan—
blindly believing in something nobody's ever seen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0042
rows.name:
Fine then! Take it! *fsssh* But I'll tell you now,
the only thing you're going to prove with what's
on there is that Golbogga never existed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0043
rows.name:
I am thrilled to hear it. *fsssh* The other Zaruboggan
have always shunned me as a pariah, so you are the
first ally I've ever known.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0044
rows.name: *fsssh* You have to find a Zaruboggan called Kiliran.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0045
rows.name:
He should be able to break the encryption which locks
this disk. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0046
rows.name:
Heh heh heh... *fsssh* Once we're inside it,
we'll finally have proof that Golbogga never existed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0050
rows.name:
Ah, comrade! Friend! Did you manage to get that
disk unlocked? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0051
rows.name:
...Yes, excellent. It appears to be completely accessible
now. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0052
rows.name:
Heh heh heh. *fsssh* Now to pull back the curtain and
reveal this conspiracy for the lie it is![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0053
rows.name:
We'll tear down the false idol of Golbogga that's stood
for millennia, and those fraudulent zealots who uphold
him with it! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0054
rows.name:
Toluera, the finest Zaruboggan biologist in history,
will at last drag the truth kicking and screaming into
the light! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0055
rows.name: Ah ha ha ha ha! *fsssh* Aaaaha ha ha... Huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0056
rows.name: *fssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0057
rows.name:
...What is this? This isn't possible... This...
*fsssh* No! I won't accept it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0058
rows.name:
My research proves that Zaruboggan evolved from
microorganisms dwelling in voltant! *fsssh* It proves...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0059
rows.name: A-and why would Golbogga look like THAT? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0090
rows.name: Inquire about Facts[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0091
rows.name: Ask what it is that Toluera refuses to accept.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0100
rows.name: Inquire about Golbogga[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0101
rows.name: Ask Toluera what Golbogga looks like.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0060
rows.name:
If what this disk says is real, then... *fsssh*
Then Golbogga really did exist.
There really was a prior civilization...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0061
rows.name:
And just before burying Bedun in a sea of voltant,
he—no, THEY engineered us as a lifeform able to
survive in that new era. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0062
rows.name:
But... *fsssh* Nrgh! Then what about all my research?
Was it all just a waste of time?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0063
rows.name: That can't be the case. *fsssh* It ISN'T the case![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0064
rows.name: But why does Golbogga look like a human? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0065
rows.name:
Golbogga does not exist... MUSTN'T exist! *fsssh*
These records are falsified! Lies, all of them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0066
rows.name:
Otherwise it would mean all my research was wasted.
It would mean Feloran's rantings were right! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0067
rows.name: I don't believe it... *fsssh* I refuse to believe it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0068
rows.name:
And why would Golbogga look like that? *fsssh*
Why would he be identical to a human?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0069
rows.name:
You... You did this! *fsssh* Else you're here in the same
form as Golbogga just to mock me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0070
rows.name:
Go then! Begone! Take this, if it will make you leave!
*fsssh* I'm not wrong. I know I'm not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0071
rows.name:
...Or are you planning to flood this planet with voltant
as before? *fsssh* Will you create more warped life?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0072
rows.name:
What gives you the right?! *fsssh* Do you interfere with
natural evolution and reject its authority just so you can
style yourselves as gods?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0110
rows.name: Agree[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0111
rows.name: Say humanity has that right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0120
rows.name: Deny[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0121
rows.name: Protest that humans aren't that narcissistic.

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0073
rows.name:
Such unbridled ego! *fsssh* Alas, Mira is truly doomed.
You'll cover her in voltant and give birth to the next
Zaruboggan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0074
rows.name:
*fsssh* More twisted, hollow life cast adrift from the
natural order.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0075
rows.name:
No... Everyone's just trying to deceive me! *fsssh*
I'm sure this disk is also fake. There is no creator.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0076
rows.name:
Rrrgh! I wish all the voltant on Mira would vanish
and the Zaruboggan would die out! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0077
rows.name:
RAAAAAAAAAAAGH! I can't... I can't!
*fsssh* *fsssh* *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0001
rows.name: Nnnh... Oh. *fsssh* Now I've begun seeing things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0002
rows.name:
But why would I see a mirage human, of all things?
*fsssh* Very strange...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0010
rows.name: Explain

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Toluera that you aren't a mirage.

rows.label: qev061002_JNK0020
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev061002_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Toluera to explain his situation.

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0003
rows.name:
*fsssh* Now the mirage is explaining its own existence.
...And rather lucidly at that. Fascinating.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0004
rows.name:
*fsssh* Now the mirage is asking questions...
Fascinating.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0005
rows.name: It has been too long since my last devoltanizing. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0006
rows.name: I've gone through all the voltant I stockpiled. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0007
rows.name:
There. I answered your question, mirage. *fsssh*
Now have the grace to vanish in a wisp of smoke.
Keeping my...eyes open is too much effort...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0008
rows.name: *fsssh* ...Wh-what's that? Not a mirage?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0009
rows.name:
Ha ha! I won't be fooled. If you think I'll go believing
people exist with zero evidence to support it,
you have me confused with my fool brethren. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0010
rows.name:
Well, if you're not vanishing, I may as well hold on
long enough for one last conversation. *fsssh*
Why have you come here, mirage?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0011
rows.name:
*fsssh* ...What? You want me to hand over Golbogga's
legacy? Awfully presumptuous for an illusion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0012
rows.name:
But fine. *fsssh* Bring me a zirtodiamond packed full of
highly condensed voltant, and it's yours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0013
rows.name:
I stole it from their cathedral to prove Golbogga never
existed...but I don't suppose it matters now. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0014
rows.name:
If I don't devoltanize soon, that and any other
ambitions I hold will die with me. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0015
rows.name:
Aah... My body feels dry as dust. *fsssh*
I'm fading fast...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0016
rows.name:
Mirage, ghost, I don't care what you are... *fsssh*
Please bring me a zirtodiamond. Hurry...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0047
rows.name: I will continue my research here. *fsssh* Alone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0048
rows.name:
Golbogga does not exist. I'm certain of it. *fsssh*
I'll open the others' eyes to that fact someday.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0049
rows.name:
Please, you must find Kiliran. I don't know where he is,
exactly, save for somewhere here on Mira. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061002_MSG0078
rows.name:
Heh. We'll disprove the myth of Golbogga together,
you and I! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
